## Summary

This documentation covers Amplitude Experiment's client-side Android SDK implementation, including installation via Maven Central, initialization with Amplitude Analytics or third-party integrations, remote/local evaluation methods (fetch/start), variant access, exposure tracking, and configuration options for features like automatic exposure tracking, bootstrapping, and user/exposure tracking providers.

